,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ce768b4249ec55c209dd76616ee10e83d5b3ffb","tid":2198573,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:32:46.000Z","msg":"佢真係覺得少咗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e2ab955c3365447098b3708217a4f70b65bb23","tid":2198573,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"習總見Trump又係咪勾結外國勢力?"},{"pid":"81dda48d2d2e2fa097b70f0af0d25ba08b1998f7","tid":2198573,"uid":346701,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"quote":{"pid":"67805303011cc9ea888a58149cb3334c794ffd0f","tid":2198573,"uid":179775,"like":44,"dislike":14,"score":30,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"老公打老婆 <br />\n老婆走佬去朋友屋企<br />\n<br />\n老公屌佢有外部勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"拐子佬拐咗人地個女<br />\n迫個女去做野搵錢比自己<br />\n家下拐子佬仲強姦女<br />\n隔離屋睇唔過眼<br />\n拐子佬話「強姦個女係我家事，外人不得說三道四」<br />\n<br />\n個女向其他隔居叫救命<br />\n拐子佬「串通其他外人干涉家庭內部事務」<br />\n<br />\n其他隔居屌柒個拐子佬<br />\n拐子佬「強烈譴責其他外人干涉我家事」"},{"pid":"b7cfa04a851a941ad2cfc3ade45a8cf431886734","tid":2198573,"uid":36901,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"2002年，李家超被借調至保安局，以研究有關電腦罪行的立法等事宜，回歸警務處後領導投訴及內部調查科投訴警察課。<span class=\"red\">翌年，李家超獲警務處保送至英國倫敦的皇家防衛學院</span>（英語：Royal College of Defence Studies）深造，回流香港後獲晉升為警務處助理處長，出任西九龍總區指揮官。<br />\n<br />\n死漢奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03529a6598f288e0d726acbd0f61298d041f767c","tid":2198573,"uid":255497,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26c53cefbd6bcf896b0cdde3b5058b0ad6d86de8","tid":2198573,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"咁嘅邏輯都可以做高官？"},{"pid":"0ae6daa5b2fc502af3e5c2e17bbfbb38ed794d4d","tid":2198573,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"I understand his feeling now <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ee79677d2302f0122778e5b2cf64cc7fbde619","tid":2198573,"uid":152705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"33ba7dcdf6b5d9380c2af8229baa210308f56f59","tid":2198573,"uid":35112,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:26:35.000Z","msg":"佢條眉真喺 好古裝片青樓做果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"真係公公相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8f182b0d097c444838950a64bd3bc4c72944ac","tid":2198573,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:43:15.000Z","msg":"鎖國呀笨"},{"pid":"d2193b7c9753eb72d3ea8b494b2939a2e549f526","tid":2198573,"uid":265867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"呢個奄人"},{"pid":"10dbbdb5e1ad5ec8c2247c386a918b3eb4cc222b","tid":2198573,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bb7293987586850a77928e3c1601371dc8ab2e8","tid":2198573,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:24:00.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超接受電視專訪，稱現時看得很清楚，外部勢力已深入香港，因港獨分子去外國獲高級官員接見，而且公然要求外國制裁，亦不是一般市民的訴求，強調港區國安法實施後，亦有人退場、退休等，證明他們以往所為，就是港區國安法所針對的行為。<br />\n<br />\n李家超在訪問中又指，自從港區國安法實施後，勾結及外部勢力參與減少很多，惟不能掉以輕心，直言中國與西方博奕仍然發生，香港需要做好本份，將港區國安法執行及落實好，令社會太平穩定、恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，港區國安法的實施，更重要是改變國家安全及國家意識，讓人明白國家安全是一定要保護、所有香港人都有義務，而且要明白港獨是犯法行為，需要因而坐牢，反問若然沒有立法，如何進行教育工作。<br />\n<br />\n李家超強調，中央在制定港區國安法，「其實很客氣」，是對香港整體有關愛的心，因為不設追溯力，而且只針對香港具體情況，與內地國安法相比，只是針對4項罪行，是很小的範圍。對於中央保留管轄權，李家超認為中央只是保留權利，去確保極端情況下擁有效手段處理，但有信心香港危害國家安全風險會下降，需要中央介入的可能性亦愈來愈低。<br />\n<br />\n自港區國安法實施後，有西方國家暫緩與港引渡。李家超批評是政治凌駕法治，直言感到遺憾，認為會發放非常錯誤信息予在港犯法人士，只要離開香港便毋須負起法律責任，在道德上亦是非常不要得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2750000/2750835/04_600.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2750000%2F2750835%2F04_600.jpeg&h=a3958520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李家超接受專訪時稱，中央就制定港區國安法是對香港關愛。（鳳凰衛視提供）<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2750835</code></pre>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:53:02.000Z","msg":"一定講緊NATHAN LAW"},{"pid":"32713b03353828cdbd44f59ca7226911e9c4a3ea","tid":2198573,"uid":188411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"Pelosi 親共的，所以黃之鋒係手足嚟啊比卡超<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6219aac1f3efd8ef11499d7210ae1062672fce2","tid":2198573,"uid":35354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"恐怖份子下場只有無人機"},{"pid":"cd62bcc53639fd01d35e5779ea056b27daa46b89","tid":2198573,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e74661e8d6e4e59050b3efea31be7363b1d6d7c6","tid":2198573,"uid":275243,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"好嬲好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我去都係摸門釘咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呀唔係宜家應該入唔到境<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" cla